<plot>A story about a dysfunctional Jewish family in Brooklyn. Shula and David have two sons: Nick, an alcoholic, marriage consultant who's watching his own marriage collapse and Ben, (in the closet) who's having problems with his transvestite partner, Jasmine. Not aware of Ben's sexuality, the parents decide to fix him up with a nice Jewish girl on Passover night. The supposedly innocent virgin arrives with her parents hoping to have a great time. Everything goes pretty well until Jasmine; Ben's transvestite partner arrives unexpectedly.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?276435</url></doc>
